Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comima again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be back around now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Kurisu-chan, you come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with crowded places.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be that crowded on the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come, too, Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you got back, you've been down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell Mayuri is trying to cheer you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's safe today, tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I talked to you about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:37.60,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Endless Apoptosis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri is going to die tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was the night of the 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time I undo a D-mail, it goes back a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to go with her to Comima tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a way to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait for her to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to know the precise deadline \Nin this world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can time leap back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one to undo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that Kiryuu Moeka person's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what she sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sent a message
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,telling herself not to buy a new cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I need to send it from her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with Mayuri to Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can protect Mayuri before she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't find Moeka, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can tell me anything, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter when, come talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what world line you're in, \Nyou aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.43,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:37.14,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Assistant\NSubject: Now in Ariake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm in Ariake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No response from Moeka, but I found her workplace."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll check it out."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiryuu Moeka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. That chick who worked here \Ntwo or three days and quit. That was her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her address?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have it. But who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.02,Sign19A,,0000,0000,0000,,Heights White
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.81,Sign19A,,0000,0000,0000,,Heights White 202 \NKiryuu Moeka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiryuu Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She killed herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body was taken to Chiyoda Hospital 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to have any relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did her companions kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before she could kill Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, Mayuri will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A time leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to time leap to before Moeka dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oka... Okabe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri... Mayuri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline is 19:52.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the label!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "Makise" right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a girl named Kiryuu Moeka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did a time leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.18,Sign19A,,0000,0000,0000,,Heights White
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you message me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiryuu Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did what you wanted... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your orders, FB!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. No... No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.14,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Makise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the D-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in Braun's TV Workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 42" is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu! Activate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.97,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your phone. It will sell out soon,\Nand you won't be able to get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I send this, Mayuri will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you send it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Reading Steiner didn't activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Reading Steiner didn't activate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The D-mail works differently, \Ndepending on who it was sent to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean your message \Nwon't change her actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't change her cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You confirmed it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I changed my cell phone four days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I want to tell myself not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sent another just after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means we don't know \Nwhat was in that D-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be in her outbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to call you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what are they doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Couples these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to make you give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember sending a D-Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A D... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have received a strange message
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from your future self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what it said! And I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Can't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have something to do with the IBN 5100?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Rounders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want your cell phone back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't betray them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That FB person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get my orders from FB.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB is everything to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't betray FB?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you're so loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't give a damn about \Nwhat happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't contacted you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been betrayed. Cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.39,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,...in Cabinet Office...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been used!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:13.35,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Rounder Recruitment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why you can tell me these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FB is like a mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.77,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: A Question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What kind of job is it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:25.20,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Re: A Question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a type of time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The message from the future is proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.16,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Another Question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can I do it, too?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:31.12,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Re: Another Question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:31.12,Sign19B,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. We offer everyone \Nthe job that best suits them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They needed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've never worked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no skills or things I'm good at."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.79,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:40.25,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will kill yourself in this room, \Nfour days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die here, alone, \Nstill waiting to hear from FB!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never hear from FB again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been waiting a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this dark, empty room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed Mayuri. And now you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, betrayed, like a piece of garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even FB!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said they were like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is FB a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, they'd hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the look of it, I bet you've never \Nspoken by phone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you did anything they ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave me a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.47,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,The retro-PC is in Yanabayashi Shrine. \NRecover it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the one who stole the IBN 5100...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Moeka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll undo the D-mail, as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,July 31st, around 11:00 AM, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:59.06,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go to the shrine. \NIt's a trap. It isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kiryuu Moeka from the past \Ndidn't believe the D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She believed the first one, just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could try another message!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's only one person she'll follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I send a message from that phone, she'll obey it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for FB.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she does, she won't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you were saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I killed someone. Is that in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do it if FB ordered you to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you knew you were being used?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die... \NAbandoned, still longing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four days. August 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world itself has decided that you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no avoiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coin locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the Daibiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The IBN 5100...
